features: 🔒Passcode Entry: Passcode Entry: This keypad lock offers 20 access codes for family use and a temporary code for single-use guest entry.
🔒One-Time Code: A one-time PIN code can be set for door opening and will automatically be deleted after use.
🔒Smart-Locking: Features an automatic door lock that can be set to lock in 10-99 seconds and one-touch auto-lock by pressing and holding any key on the keypad for 2 seconds.

🔒Security Deadbolt: Provides reliable home protection with its sturdy aluminum alloy construction, weather resistance (IP54), durability, anti-peeping user code protection, low battery indicator, and solid lock cylinder. Our deadbolt smart lock is only suitable for 2-1/8" (54mm) door holes, and is not compatible with 38mm door holes.
🔒Easy Installation: TEEHO door lock can be installed in minutes with just a screwdriver and is suitable for both men and women;

🔒Satisfaction Guaranteed: Comes with a 30-day money-back guarantee, free replacement in 1 year, and lifetime after-sales customer service from the date of purchase, including online phone support from Monday to Friday 9 AM to 5 PM EST and 24/7 online after-sales email service.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy Installation and Works Great
reviews.reviewText: Our previous keypad was over 8 years old and not working properly anymore so, it was finally time to replace it.I am pretty handy when it comes to having to replace certain things in the house, but I was not super confident if I could install this. But it had to be done and after following a YouTube video on how to install it (I personally do better with video instructions than image ones if I can find it), I was able to replace it successfully. It was easy to change the code and unlocks/locks well.My only small nitpick is that I am not a fan of the two beep noises it makes even when opening and closing the door from the inside. But that really is the only con and hopefully I will get use to it. Overall though, great price and works well!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great key pad lock and a great price!
reviews.reviewText: We wanted something so the kids could easily get into the house when they needed to without having to carry a key that got stuck a lot around. This was easy to install. It works a lot better than the key lock we had, and makes it easy for the everyone in the family to get in the house. The auto lock feature is a bonus as well. I wish more color options were available, but it is fine.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Nice looking lock. Easy to install. The code reset procedures were inaccurate when it came to the batteries and when to remove; I had to call support but they gave me the correct procedures. Has worked well since install.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for the price
reviews.reviewText: For not being top of the line, these are pretty good. Over the years we have replaced doors, locks and ended up with way too many keys and i got sick of fumbling for the right key. Replaced all of the deadbolts on house, garage and barn with these and have been super happy. The instructions could be a little better, but once I got through the first one they are breeze to install.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great deadbolt replacement
reviews.reviewText: Nice and easy installation. Easy to program up to 20 pin codes. Can be set to lock automatically when you leave. Very good quality parts. Sturdy. Works flawlessly. Fast delivery.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install and use
reviews.reviewText: Instructions are a little confusing, but if you've ever installed a dead bolt before, this is pretty much the same thing besides the batteries and the little bit of programming to get the lock/unlock orientation. Works great, even in the winter with frost on the inside door handle! Much easier than dealing with finding your keys, just a 4 digit code and I'm in the house! Would buy again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The product is nice looking and works great. The install process was easy and simple. I have had no functionality issues even with the recent cold weather. Great value for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Decent door lock. It locks and unlocks just like it's supposed to.
reviews.reviewText: This door lock works very well. I put this on my shop door so I wouldn't have to always have the key on me. It was easy to install and works well. I've had it for about 6 months and the batteries are still good although I don't unlock/lock the door everyday. Pleased with the purchase so far.

It's only been 10 days since installation, but it's working perfectly fine. The setup was easy, and it was easily mounted in place of the old lock from a different brand. The price-performance ratio is quite good in a short period.
Muy practica cerradura. Funciona perfectamente. No tuve que llamar cerrajero, es simple de colocar. Hasta ahora todo bien.
I replaced exting lock which had battery and connectivity issues with this one.Has worked for last 4 months without any fails.Seems like locks with apps are more prone for failure.

Overall seems like a good quality product but a little early to tell. Install was very simple, all parts for all situations included. Programming was fairly seamless but several steps involved, overall though programming went smooth. Happy so far.
